<subSubSection pageId="266" pageNumber="871" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="266.[1397,2605,2263,3085]" pageId="266" pageNumber="871">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1399,1746,2972,3006]" pageId="266" pageNumber="871">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Not assessed on The IUCN Red List. Christina’s Margareta Rat is likely threatened by logging.
</paragraph>
